{"tid":2265290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰機師、空服員「齊上齊落」","createTime":"2020-10-31T10:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T09:07:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c311f11ef736b990fa07c458194ae9aa86cc6e0","tid":2265290,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/KIRTDCJTX5GWXC24CEW6OHKCQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FKIRTDCJTX5GWXC24CEW6OHKCQI%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=103fb1d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FKIRTDCJTX5GWXC24CEW6OHKCQI%2F&h=9a212587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/KIRTDCJTX5GWXC24CEW6OHKCQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國泰機師、空服員「齊上齊落」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國泰航空大裁員5,300名駐港員工，並要求留任員工簽署變相減薪的「不平等合約」，最遲須於下周三前決定，若不簽約將被解僱。國泰空中服務員工會與香港航空機組人員協會表示，雙方同意往後採取聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NvwJGbBeJcQazuOc2so1WEQgc5s=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LO5Q635AEBDZ7ASQ6QOF5PQDPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNvwJGbBeJcQazuOc2so1WEQgc5s%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLO5Q635AEBDZ7ASQ6QOF5PQDPE.jpg&h=b5449212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港航空機組人員協會昨直指國泰無情，並要求與國泰及勞工處會談。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機師促延簽約死線<br />\n<br />\n國泰解僱的員工中，有600名是機師，倖存的機師也面臨大幅減薪、減福利。逾2,200名駐港國泰機師會員的香港航空機組人員協會（HKAOA）。秘書長Chris Beebe稱，國泰未有考慮個人狀況、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nBeebe續說，駐港機師是香港員工，協會不容許資方因中短期的疫潮而作。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n工會表示暫時未知道有多少名機師已經接受新合約，Beebe批評國泰提出的方案完全不切實際，而機師正面對的是職業生涯中最重要的抉擇，重申只得7至14天時間考慮並不合理，要求國泰延長簽約死線。<br />\n<br />\n國泰晚上發聲明稱已邀HKAOA會面，雙方同意下周三開會。國泰重申，下周三晚上11時59分是簽署合約的期限。<br />\n<br />\n另外，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1c7c20535a678bbcc6b54a823d6b6d09490e53c5","tid":2265290,"uid":323740,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"7-14日都話唔夠時間考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef913f9b5aa3862252483fcfc9b0a58a36e9182","tid":2265290,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩下慢, 三下快<br />\n兩下慢, 三下快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1afa183de3f4819d27e41d0f7d17c43e3829e76","tid":2265290,"uid":69976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7c20535a678bbcc6b54a823d6b6d09490e53c5","tid":2265290,"uid":323740,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"7-14日都話唔夠時間考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"擺明唔想減人工"},{"pid":"6c979bd65ee199b6f26f3c590c0e8c63dd92d758","tid":2265290,"uid":119897,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f1afa183de3f4819d27e41d0f7d17c43e3829e76","tid":2265290,"uid":69976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7c20535a678bbcc6b54a823d6b6d09490e53c5","tid":2265290,"uid":323740,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"7-14日都話唔夠時間考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"擺明唔想減人工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"佢哋有得揀咩<br />\n莊閑都未分清楚<br />\n根本依定就白養你地半年搏復蘇到"},{"pid":"9d8699bec8bb3374f84bfc2979cafa551dcec996","tid":2265290,"uid":133398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c979bd65ee199b6f26f3c590c0e8c63dd92d758","tid":2265290,"uid":119897,"